quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  26,181,"Humnee …ìetu ngun, wata on laato jeyaa…ìe e uytoo…ìe …ìen"
  26,182,Manndikiree(peesre) manndikir…óe feewu…óe …óen
  26,183,"Wata on ustan yim…ìe …ìen piiji ma…ì…ìe …óin, wata on lancito ka leydi hara ko on bonnoo…ìe"
  26,184,"Hulee On Tagu…óo on, o tagu adinoongu ngun"
  26,185,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Pellet, an ko a jeyaa…óo mbil…óaa…ìe …ìen"
  26,186,"An a wonaali si wanaa …ìanndunke yeru amen, tawde me…óen jikkumaa ko a jeyaa…óo e fenu…ìe …ìen"
  26,187,"Awa fukku e dow amen kunte kammu ngun, si tawii a laatike jeyaa…óo e goongu…ìe …ìen"
  26,188,"O maaki: \"Ko Joomi am woni Anndu…óo ko golloton kon"
  26,189,"∆Åe fenni mo, nanngi …ìe Lepte √±alaande …óowdiinde nden. Pellet, …óen laatino Lepte √±alaande mawnde"
  26,190,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ìur…ìe heewu…ìe e ma…ì…ìe laataaki gom…óin…ìe"
  26,191,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,192,"E pellet, kayre ko nde jippinaande Jooma winndere nden"
  26,193,Jippinii nde Ruuhu hoolaa…óo on
  26,194,Ka …ìernde maa…óa fii yo a laato jeyaa…óo e jertinoo…ìe …ìen
  26,195,E …óemngal Aarabu …ìanngungal
  26,196,"Pellet, kayre hinde ka …óeri aran…ìe …ìen"
  26,197,"Enee, hara laatanaaki …ìe Maande, nde tawata anndiino nde …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila anndu…ìe …ìen"
  26,198,Sinndo Men jippinno nde e dow yoga e ajamiyankoo…ìe …ìen
  26,199,"o janngi nde e dow ma…ì…ìe, …ìe laatotaako gom…óin…ìe nde"
  26,200,Ko wano nii Men naadiri …óum e …ìer…óe bon…ìe …ìen
  26,201,"∆Åe gom…óintaa nde, haa …ìe yi'a Lepte muusu…óe …óen"
  26,202,"∆äe ara e ma…ì…ìe e juhayee, hara …ìe so'aa"
  26,203,"Sakko …ìe wi'a: \"Taw si ko men nennantee…ìe"
  26,204,"Enee, ko Lepte Amen …óen …ìe he√±orta"
  26,205,A tinii si Men dakmitii …ìe duu…ìi
  26,206,Refti ari e ma…ì…ìe kon ko …ìe laatinoo hi…ìe fodee
  26,207,Nafaali …ìe ko …ìe laatinoo kon hi…ìe dakmitoo
  26,208,"Men halkaali saare woo, si wanaa hara no woodani nde jertinoo…ìe"
  26,209,"[∆äum] ko waaju, Men laataaki too√±oo…ìe"
  26,210,Wanaa seytanuuji …óin jippini nde
  26,211,"[∆äum] haananaa…ói, …ói hattantaake kadi"
  26,212,"Pellet, kannji ko …ói follatee…ói gaayi he…óagol ngol"
  26,213,"Wata a noddu rewetee…óo goo wonndude e Alla, sakko laato…óaa jeyaa…óo e Leptetee…ìe …ìen"
  26,214,Jertin gorol maa…óa …ìur…ìe …ìadaade …ìen
  26,215,"Les…óinan balbe maa…óen, wonannde …ìen jokku…ìe ma immorde e gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  26,216,"Si …ìe yeddii ma, haray maaku: \"Min dey, ko mi danndii…óo kon ko golloton"
  26,217,Hoolor On Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo
  26,218,On Sutii…óo ma fewndo daroto…óaa
  26,219,E waylitogol maa…óa e hakkunde sujjoo…ìe …ìen
  26,220,"Pellet, ko Kanko woni Nanoowo Anndu…óo On"
  26,221,Taw si mi humpitay on ko e hommbo Seytanuuji …óin jippotoo
  26,222,Hi…ói jippoo e dow kala fefindotoo…óo bakkodin…óo
  26,223,"Hi…ói werloo nan…óe …óen, ko …ìur…ìe heewude e majji ko fenooji"
  26,224,"Yimoo…ìe …ìen ko jokkata …ìe, ko bew…ìe …ìen"
  26,225,"Enee, a tinaali wonndema kam…ìe hi…ìe yinoo e kala aynde"
  26,226,E tawde kam…ìe hi…ìe wowla ko …ìe huuwataa
  26,227,Si wanaa …ìen gom…óin…ìe …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e …ìe ja≈ãtii Alla ko …óuu…ói …ìe yo…ìtii …ìaawo …ìe too√±aama. Aray ka …ìen too√±u…ìe annday ko honde e waylitorde …ìe waylitotoo